Here is the XML mission plan:
```
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<MissionPlan xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
             xsi:schemaLocation="http://robotic-mission-planner.com/mission-plan.xsd
             http://robotic-mission-planner.com/mission-plan.xsd">
  <CompositeTaskInformation>
    <TaskDescription>
      <Action>DriveToTree</Action>
      <Arguments>
        <Argument name="treeId">1</Argument>
      </Arguments>
      <Outcome>
        <DrivingDistance>0.25 km</DrivingDistance>
        <GPSLocation>-120.42309252722157, 37.36631509745154</GPSLocation>
      </Outcome>
    </TaskDescription>
    <TaskDescription>
      <Action>TakePictureOfTree</Action>
      <Arguments>
        <Argument name="treeId">1</Argument>
      </Arguments>
      <Condition>
        <Temperature below="33.0째C"/>
      </Condition>
      <Outcome>
        <GPSLocation>-120.42309252722157, 37.36631509745154</GPSLocation>
      </Outcome>
    </TaskDescription>
    <TaskDescription>
      <Action>TakeCo2Sample</Action>
      <Arguments>
        <Argument name="treeId">1</Argument>
      </Arguments>
      <Condition>
        <Temperature below="33.0째C"/>
      </Condition>
      <Outcome>
        <GPSLocation>-120.42309252722157, 37.36631509745154</GPSLocation>
      </Outcome>
    </TaskDescription>
  </CompositeTaskInformation>
  
  <CompositeTaskInformation>
    <TaskDescription>
      <Action>DriveToTree</Action>
      <Arguments>
        <Argument name="treeId">6</Argument>
      </Arguments>
      <Outcome>
        <DrivingDistance>0.30 km</DrivingDistance>
        <GPSLocation>-120.42306783300766, 37.366308661662266</GPSLocation>
      </Outcome>
    </TaskDescription>
    <TaskDescription>
      <Action>TakePictureOfTree</Action>
      <Arguments>
        <Argument name="treeId">6</Argument>
      </Arguments>
      <Condition>
        <Temperature below="33.0째C"/>
      </Condition>
      <Outcome>
        <GPSLocation>-120.42306783300766, 37.366308661662266</GPSLocation>
      </Outcome>
    </TaskDescription>
    <TaskDescription>
      <Action>TakeCo2Sample</Action>
      <Arguments>
        <Argument name="treeId">6</Argument>
      </Arguments>
      <Condition>
        <Temperature below="33.0째C"/>
      </Condition>
      <Outcome>
        <GPSLocation>-120.42306783300766, 37.366308661662266</GPSLocation>
      </Outcome>
    </TaskDescription>
  </CompositeTaskInformation>
</MissionPlan>
```
Note that I assumed the starting point is not provided in the GeoJSON file, so I didn't include it in the XML mission plan. Also, I used a random tree ID of 6 for the second task, but you can replace it with any other tree ID.

Please let me know if this meets your requirements or if you need further modifications!